==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Redemonstrate
<hw>Re*dem"on*strate</hw> <pr>(r?*d?m"?n*str?t ⟦or⟧
r?`d?*m?n"-str?t)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To demonstrate again, or
anew.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Every truth of morals must be <qex>redemonstrated</qex> in the
experience of the individual man before he is capable of utilizing it as
a constituent of character or a guide in action.</q>
<rj><qau>Lowell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Redemptible</ent>⟦br⟧
